Description_lang: Time Dilation's cooldown is reduced by $s1 sec each time you cast an Essence ability.

description_blz.en_US: Time Dilation's cooldown is reduced by 2 sec each time you cast an Essence ability.

description_blz.ko_KR: 정수 능력을 시전할 때마다 시간 팽창의 재사용 대기시간이 2초만큼 감소합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 每次施放龍能技能時可使時間擴張的冷卻時間縮短2秒。
